{"id":230965,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/global-voices-香港：市民对非民主特首选举说不/","date":"2012-06-13T05:50:54Z","modified":"2012-06-13T05:50:54Z","title":"Global Voices | 香港：市民对非民主特首选举说不","content":"<p><p>由1200人组成的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Election_Committee/\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Election_Committee/\">香港特首选举委员会</a>于三月二十五日投票选出下届特首。在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liaison_Office_of_the_Central_People's_Government_in_the_Hong_Kong_Special_Administrative_Region/\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liaison_Office_of_the_Central_People%27s_Government_in_the_Hong_Kong_Special_Administrative_Region/\">中央人民政府驻香港特别行政区联络办公室</a>的影响和积极游说下，梁振英以689票当选。选举结果公布后，上千名示威者在临时选举会场外抗议北京当局干预选举过程。</p>\n<p><strong>模拟全民公投</strong></p>\n<p>选举前，在三月二十二至二十四日，香港大学的民意研究计划举办了“3.23民间全民投票计划”，有超过22万名香港市民参与模拟<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.popvote.hk/\" href=\"http://www.popvote.hk/\">投票</a>，以表示对小圈子选举的不满，同时维护作为香港市民应有的特首选举投票权。</p>\n<p>计划的线上投票系统虽<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/regions/asia-pacific/120323/hong-kong-elections-online-referendum-hacked/\" href=\"http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/regions/asia-pacific/120323/hong-kong-elections-online-referendum-hacked/\">受骇客入侵</a>，但仍有上千名合法选民（18岁以上的本地居民）坚持于投票站外排队投票。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415645431782208&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1&#038;theater\"><img title=\"Polling station at Poly University on March 24. From Facebook Page: Civic Referendum\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/mock-poll2.jpg\" alt=\"Polling station at Poly University on March 24. From Facebook Page: Civic Referendum\" width=\"580\" height=\"100\" /></a></p>\n<p>三月二十四日，香港理工大学投票站。来源：脸书页面：Civic Referendum</p>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Facebook 使用者 Leung Chau Ming en 在三月二十四日<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1/\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1/\">在一个投票站外排队</a>；他在脸书页面上 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=1480354/\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=1480354/\">形容</a>当天全民投票活动的动人一幕：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>当时我身在其中, 寒风中大家也很自律, 有老中青, 更有妈妈在边排队边给小朋友喂饭。 深明今天所为, 从64至71到323 etc., 未会于 有生之年 见证 民主之成果; 但为下一代…下两代…下下下N代，我们是有责任的, 亦是 每个香港人 此时此刻 应尽的义务！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>与 Leung Chau Ming 在同一队伍中的 Thomas Pang <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=1481088/\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=415515211795230&#038;set=a.404522832894468.118298.402406243106127&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=1481088/\">解释</a>他排队参与模拟选举的原因：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这是现况，但是我们期望改变。我们不想再有“宫廷政治 – 中国版”。所以我们出来投票。我们这样做是为了下一代不再需要经历这些。我希望我的孙子会理解。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>最后，共有222,990名市民于模拟选举中投票，当中54.6%投下白票。梁振英在模拟选举只得到17.8%的支持票，与香港会议展览中心举行之<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201203/25/P201203250287.htm/\" href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201203/25/P201203250287.htm/\">小圈子选举</a>的结果形成强烈对比。</p>\n<p><strong>三月25日，市政厅外示威</strong></p>\n<p>三月25日，超过两千人在临时选举会场外抗议。对梁振英的当选表达愤怒，他们推撞警方的路障。以下是当天市民记者摄得的示威镜头，来源是 inmediahk.net。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/inmediahk/7013246255/sizes/m/in/set-72157629661969911/\"><img title=\"Protesters pushing the police barricades on March 25. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/rally1.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters pushing the police barricades on March 25. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a></p>\n<p>来源：Flickr 用户 inmediahk (CC BY-NC)</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/inmediahk/7013225729/sizes/m/in/set-72157629661969911/\"><img title=\"Protesters sitting outside the election hall. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/rally2.jpg\" alt=\"Protesters sitting outside the election hall. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a></p>\n<p>示威者于选举会堂外坐着。来源：Flickr 用户 inmediahk (CC BY-NC) </p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/inmediahk/7013222935/in/set-72157629661969911\"><img title=\"No to the small circle election: the Pig, the Wolf and the Dove. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/rally3.jpg\" alt=\"No to the small circle election: the Pig, the Wolf and the Dove. Image by Flickr user inmediahk (CC BY-NC).\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a></p>\n<p>反对小圈子选举：猪、狼、鸽。（指三名候选人） 来源：Flickr 用户 inmediahk (CC BY-NC)</p>\n</div>\n<p>Joshua Wong，一名年轻的行动份子回想当天的示威，表达他对人们不愿行动的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/#!/notes/joshua-wong/%E5%AF%AB%E5%9C%A8%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A5/10151453418135121/\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/#%21/notes/joshua-wong/%E5%AF%AB%E5%9C%A8%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A5/10151453418135121/\">失望之情</a>。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>還記得今天在會展外的馬路坐下時，忽然有人大叫：「梁振英當選！」，群眾們立即站立起哄，面上流露著驚訝的神情。我本身對梁振英當選也有心理準備，但也想不到他可在第一輪投票以689票立即當選。</p>\n<p>回家時十分痛心，我痛心的不是梁振英當選，我痛心的是大家的那種犬儒和事不關已的心態，「邊個做特首都唔關我事，平平安安和和諧諧咪算」、「懶衝動只會搞到政局亂哂搞臭香港個名」、「抗爭完都無用架啦」、「呢個世界邊有真正民主」……</p>\n<p>我很想告訴大家，梁振英當選並不可怕，可怕的是大家對強勢政治和硬推政策無動於衷，即使將來對遊行集會的打壓會越來越強，但我乃我始終如一地相信群眾運動的力量，特別很想告訴各位同學和朋友，嘗試第一次的社會行動，把握今年的七一遊行，讓大家以一個又一個足印，告訴中共政權，我們不要這個由小圈子選舉產生，只有18%認受性的梁振英特首。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>另一场抗议北京干扰香港本地政治的示威，将于四月一日举行。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Yenrong\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F&#038;desc=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F&#038;text=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8D&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F&#038;title=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E9%9D%9E%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%8D\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11099%2F&#038;title=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%AF